{"tid":2249504,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌臭FIFA 21 ？","createTime":"2020-10-19T11:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T10:55:55.000Z","uid":368642,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ba3b9584bd20b0dcb0134d35a790b3e5900c2adf","tid":2249504,"uid":368642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:20:28.000Z","msg":"講下自己背景先！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一開接觸FIFA14之後keep住單機打<br />\n由FIFA 17轉打online division 打到21，<br />\n唔算差，起碼打到上D1<br />\n*冇玩UT(無時間炒卡)。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一開始諗住FIFA 21應該幾正，<br />\n開左第一場波就後悔洗左3舊幾水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n21相比於20<br />\n進攻：<br />\n屈數據，屈速度，場場大上大落，<br />\n主要放長波，直傳，跑！<br />\n<br />\n防守：<br />\n中場失位，明明邊路有人，Default將個閘位拉去中場補，哭撚左<br />\n<br />\n覺得FIFA20嘅戰術多元化好多，控球、反擊、長傳、打柱躉，唔同嘅戰術都打到，主要睇重自己嘅操作<br />\n<br />\n仲有～<br />\n<span class=\"red\">屌你老母EA！現實場場波都咁大比數咩？！</span><br />\n打左廿場，我未撚試過有一場總入波細過4波<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9586dde8f0a580f23ce50a9d6d0399bcbaca4e84","tid":2249504,"uid":169906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:28:12.000Z","msg":"算啦 鬧完都係會繼續打Fifa"},{"pid":"a75710222512a8da3474f0c71cb0e074b4ce4c3b","tid":2249504,"uid":138736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:29:40.000Z","msg":"屌完然後繼續打下一舖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8955e7680dac3b19f5b1be3fc64b7e6ef